        <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i> Easily calculate taxes based on <strong>seat capacity and applicable rates</strong>.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i> <strong>File returns</strong> with no hassle of lengthy paperwork.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i> Access <strong>historical payment records</strong> for auditing purposes.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>


<!-- Tax Information Section -->
<div class="container-fluid mt-4 mb-5 ">
    <div class=" shadow-sm border-0 bg-light p-4 mx-auto w-100">
        <div class="body">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark text-center mb-4"><i class="fas fa-ticket-alt text-primary"></i> Theatre Tax Information</h2>
            <p class="text-muted fs-5 text-center mb-5">Understanding theatre tax is essential for smooth operations. Below are key points regarding theatre taxation:</p>

            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                <!-- First Item -->
                <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center border-0 bg-white mb-3 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center bg-primary text-white me-3" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                        <i class="fas fa-chair fs-4"></i>
                    </div>
                    <span class="fs-5">All registered theatres must pay taxes based on seat capacity and screen operations.</span>
                </li>
                <!-- Second Item -->
                <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center border-0 bg-white mb-3 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center bg-primary text-white me-3" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt fs-4"></i>
                    </div>
